HEADWORD: lachrymator
<hw>lachrymator</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A chemical substance that causes
tears to flow; same as <er>lacrimator</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> lacrimator.</syn>⟦br⟧
